  <p>We respect your privacy. This policy explains how our app handles your data.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>Workout sessions, exercises, sets, and progress photos are stored only on your device using local storage (Hive).</p>

  <h2>2. How We Use Data</h2>
  <p>Your data is used solely to provide workout tracking and related features. We do not collect, sell, or share your personal data.</p>

  <h2>3. Camera Permissions</h2>
  <p>The app requests camera access only to let you capture progress photos. Photos are stored locally on your device and are never uploaded or shared by us.</p>

  <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not share your data with any third parties.</p>

  <h2>5. User Controls</h2>
  <p>You can clear all app data by uninstalling the app or resetting it in device settings.</p>

  <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>If we introduce online or social features in the future, this policy will be updated to explain how your data is handled.</p>

